## Integration with Aider Features

### Auto-Commits Work Well

Aider auto-commits all changes. This integrates nicely with IdlerGear:
- Aider commits the code
- IdlerGear tracks the work (tasks)
- Git history shows what happened
- IdlerGear shows why it happened (vision, tasks)

### Test Command

You can configure Aider to run IdlerGear checks:

```yaml
# .aider.conf.yml
test-cmd: echo "Remember to track with IdlerGear!"
auto-test: false
```

